{"id":910,"parent_id":909,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":910,"title":"Amos 1","subtitle":"","short_title":"Amos","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1","content":[["div",[".title",["span.dominant","Amos"]],[".titleNumber","Chapter 1"],[".studySummary",["i","Amos shows the Lord’s judgments upon Syria, the Philistines, Tyre, Edom, and Ammon."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.1","order":"02.31.001.61075"},["b","1"],"The words of Amos, who was among the herdmen of Tekoa, which he saw concerning Israel in the days of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Uzziah"],"king of Judah, and in the days of",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"Jeroboam"],"the son of Joash king of Israel, two years before the",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_1c"},"earthquake"],"."],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.2","order":"02.31.001.61076"},["b","2"],"And he said, The",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"will",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"roar"],"from Zion, and utter his voice from Jerusalem; and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_2b"},"habitations"],"of the shepherds shall mourn, and the top of Carmel shall wither."],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.3","order":"02.31.001.61077"},["b","3"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; For three transgressions of Damascus, and for four, I will not turn away",["i","the punishment"],"thereof; because they have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"threshed"],"Gilead with threshing instruments of iron:"],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.4","order":"02.31.001.61078"},["b","4"],"But I will send a fire into the house of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"Hazael"],", which shall devour the palaces of Ben-hadad."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.5","order":"02.31.001.61079"},["b","5"],"I will break also the bar of Damascus, and cut off the inhabitant from the plain of Aven, and him that holdeth the sceptre from the house of Eden: and the people of Syria shall go into captivity unto Kir, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.6","order":"02.31.001.61080"},["b","6"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; For three transgressions of Gaza, and for four, I will not turn away",["i","the punishment"],"thereof; because they carried away captive the whole captivity, to deliver",["i","them"],"up to Edom:"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.7","order":"02.31.001.61081"},["b","7"],"But I will send a fire on the wall of Gaza, which shall devour the palaces thereof:"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.8","order":"02.31.001.61082"},["b","8"],"And I will cut off the inhabitant from",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"Ashdod"],", and him that holdeth the sceptre from Ashkelon, and I will turn mine hand against Ekron: and the remnant of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"Philistines"],"shall perish, saith the Lord",["span.smallCaps","God"],"."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.9","order":"02.31.001.61083"},["b","9"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; For three transgressions of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"Tyrus"],", and for four, I will not turn away",["i","the punishment"],"thereof; because they delivered up the whole captivity to Edom, and remembered not the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"brotherly"],"covenant:"],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.10","order":"02.31.001.61084"},["b","10"],"But I will send a fire on the wall of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"Tyrus"],", which shall devour the palaces thereof."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.11","order":"02.31.001.61085"},["b","11"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; For three transgressions of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_11a"},"Edom"],", and for four, I will not turn away",["i","the punishment"],"thereof; because he did pursue his brother with the sword, and did cast off all pity, and his anger did tear perpetually, and he kept his wrath for ever:"],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.12","order":"02.31.001.61086"},["b","12"],"But I will send a fire upon",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_12a"},"Teman"],", which shall devour the palaces of Bozrah."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.13","order":"02.31.001.61087"},["b","13"],"¶Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"; For three transgressions of the children of Ammon, and for four, I will not turn away",["i","the punishment"],"thereof; because they have ripped up the women with child of Gilead, that they might enlarge their border:"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.14","order":"02.31.001.61088"},["b","14"],"But I will kindle a fire in the wall of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_14a"},"Rabbah"],", and it shall devour the palaces thereof, with shouting in the day of battle, with a tempest in the day of the whirlwind:"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.15","order":"02.31.001.61089"},["b","15"],"And their king shall go into captivity, he and his princes together, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.1a","order":"02.31.001.61090"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/hosea/1.1"},"Hosea 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.1b","order":"02.31.001.61092"},["b","1b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/7.10"},"Amos 7:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"1c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.1c","order":"02.31.001.61094"},["b","1c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/14.5"},"Zech. 14:5"],"."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.2a","order":"02.31.001.61096"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/31.4"},"Isa. 31:4"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/25.30"},"Jer. 25:30"],"."],["div",{"id":"2b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.2b","order":"02.31.001.61098"},["b","2b"],["span.small","OR"],"pastures."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.3a","order":"02.31.001.61100"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/13.7"},"2 Kgs. 13:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.4a","order":"02.31.001.61102"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/8.12"},"2 Kgs. 8:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/10.32"},"10:32"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/13.3"},"13:3"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.8a","order":"02.31.001.61104"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/amos/3.9"},"Amos 3:9"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.8b","order":"02.31.001.61106"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/14.31.29-32"},"Isa. 14:31 (29–32)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/47.1"},"Jer. 47:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/25.15.15-16"},"Ezek. 25:15 (15–16)"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.9a","order":"02.31.001.61108"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/23.1"},"Isa. 23:1"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/26.2"},"Ezek. 26:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.9b","order":"02.31.001.61110"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/brotherhood-and-sisterhood"},"TG Brotherhood and Sisterhood"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.10a","order":"02.31.001.61112"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zech/9.3.3-4"},"Zech. 9:3 (3–4)"],"."],["div",{"id":"11a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.11a","order":"02.31.001.61114"},["b","11a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.7"},"Jer. 49:7"],"."],["div",{"id":"12a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.12a","order":"02.31.001.61116"},["b","12a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/obad/1.9.9-10"},"Obad. 1:9 (9–10)"],"."],["div",{"id":"14a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/amos/1.14a","order":"02.31.001.61118"},["b","14a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/49.2"},"Jer. 49:2"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/21.20"},"Ezek. 21:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/25.5.4-5"},"25:5 (4–5)"],"."]]}
